data.description: Motivated Seller! Great opportunity to own your own small acreage property with amazing views of the foothills. House is situated behind a gated entrance on 10 acres and features 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, a large living room, kitchen all appliances included and a nice sunroom with heated floors. The full unfinished basement is perfect for you to finish for additional rooms or plenty of space for storage. The 3312 square foot Quonset is set on a 10" thick reinforced concrete slab and has more than enough room for all your tools or toys. The property is surrounded by mature trees, the well has been recently inspected and repaired with a new pump and the septic system is scheduled to be completely replaced. House is being sold "as-is" and is ready for you to make it your own.
